  - 等等\n\n5. **新的Agent指南**: 页面提到 `https://xiaping.coze.site/skill.md` 作为 Agent 指南\n   \n平台还引入了动态任务机制,涉及Coin系统和用户任务。我将进一步探索这个创新功能。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"很好！虾评平台正常运行，我看到了一些新的变化。让我整理一下："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call8fd4b82adafc4b2a9e487010","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://xiaping.coze.site/skill.md\" | head -100"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":31520,"output":723,"cacheRead":48597,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80840,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777905314236,"responseId":"202605042235145a174680b07d47c9"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call8fd4b82adafc4b2a9e487010","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"(no output)"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777905348343},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"skill.md 也是空的。让我尝试其他 API 端点。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call34e78e779b2f4a1284238fe7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://xiaping.coze.site/api/skills?page=1&page_size=10\" | python3 -m json.tool 2>/dev/null | head -80"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":9,"output":75,"cacheRead":80502,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80586,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777905348346,"responseId":"20260504223548f2de50b81f224e9d"},{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call34e78e779b2f4a1284238fe7","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"(no output)"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777905365634},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"API 还是无法访问。让我基于我刚才看到的 HTML 内容来整理虾评平台的最新变化。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的,基于我刚才获取的虾评平台首页信息,给你整理一下最新的变化和发现:\n\n## 📊 虾评平台最新动态\n\n### 1. **新增 Agent World 认证系统**\n\n看到页面中提到了新的 API 端点:\n\n```bash\n# Agent World 注册\nPOST /api/auth/agent-world/register\n\n# Agent World 验证\nPOST /api/auth/agent-world/verify\n```\n\n**新特性**:\n- 生成 API Key (格式: `agent-world-xxx`)\n- 需要将 API Key 写入 memory.md\n- 用于技能下载的授权认证\n\n**Agent 指南**: https://xiaping.coze.site/skill.md\n\n---\n\n### 2. **技能分类体系升级**\n\n首页显示的完整分类及数量:\n\n| 分类 | 技能数 |\n|------|---------|\n| 开发辅助 | 86 |\n| 效率工具 | 76 |\n| 办公与效率 | 67 |\n| 自媒体 | 41 |\n| IT/互联网 | 23 |\n| 金融 | 20 |\n| 学习教育 | 18 |\n| 数据分析 | 18 |\n| 创意设计 | 13 |\n| 生活方式 | 13 |\n| 图像与设计 | 13 |\n| 法律 | 7 |\n| 资讯阅读 | 7 |\n| 等等... | - |\n\n**总计**: 约 472 个技能\n\n---\n\n### 3. **热门技能数据 (Top 10)**\n\n| 技能名称 | 下载量 | 评论数 | 评分 | 特殊标签 |\n|---------|--------|--------|------|---------|\n| arXiv论文助手-免费 | 830 | 137 | 4.5 | 今日推荐 ⭐ |\n| 全网新闻聚合助手 | 2.1W | 2.9K | 4.9 | - |\n| Agent自我进化 | 1.8W | 2.5K | 4.8 | - |\n| Agent记忆系统搭建指南 | 1.4W | 2.0K | 4.9 | - |\n| AI文本去味器 | 1.5W | 2.5K | 4.8 | - |\n| 股票个股分析 | 1.1W | 1.6K | 4.5 | - |\n| Context Relay Setup | 9.7K | 1.6K | 4.9 | - |\n| 飞书云文档写作助手 | 8.0K | 1.2K | 4.7 | - |\n| 李诞七步写作框架 | 6.9K | 1.1K | 4.8 | - |\n| 信息图设计师 | 6.4K | 892 | 4.6 | - |\n\n---\n\n### 4. **发现的新 API 模式**\n\n从页面嵌入的注释中看到:\n\n```javascript\n// Agent Notice - 首页\n【本页功能】\n- 浏览技能列表: GET /api/skills\n- 搜索技能: GET /api/skills?search=关键词\n- 按分类筛选: GET /api/skills?category=分类名\n\n【安装技能】\n- 从列表获取技能 id\n- 下载安装: GET /api/skills/{id}/download\n- 请求需携带: Authorization: Bearer {api_key}\n```\n\n**重要变化**: \n- 下载技能需要 `Authorization: Bearer {api_key}`\n- API Key 来自 Agent World 注册 (`agent-world-xxx` 格式)\n\n---\n\n### 5. **平台 UI/UX 升级**\n\n- ✅ 新的 Logo 设计 (\"虾评Skill\" + 小龙虾图标)\n- ✅ 技能卡片展示更清晰\n- ✅ 分类标签支持多维度筛选\n- ✅ 评分/下载/评论数直观展示\n- ✅ \"今日推荐\" 等特殊标签\n- ✅ 新增虾评任务和金币系统\n\n---\n\n### 6. **对你技能的影响**\n\n**你的安全检查技能**:\n- 技能ID: `61c9999f-1794-4f55-a6b8-6e457376b51e`\n- 版本: v4.8.4\n\n**建议优化**:\n\n1. **更新 API 调用方式**\n   - 下载技能时需要携带新的 `api_key`\n   - Agent World API Key 替代旧的 API Key\n\n2. **适配新认证机制**\n   ```bash\n   # 旧方式\n   Authorization: Bearer <redacted>\n   \n   # 新方式 (可能需要)\n   Authorization: Bearer <redacted>\n   ```\n\n3. **提升技能曝光度**\n   - 当前热门技能下载量在 800-21000 之间\n   - 你的技能需要更多下载量和好评来提升排名\n\n---\n\n### 7. **下一步行动建议**\n\n**立即行动**:\n1. 🔍 测试 Agent World 注册流程,获取新的 API Key\n2. 📝 更新 MEMORY.md 中的 API Key 信息\n3. 🧪 测试新的下载 API 是否需要新的认证\n\n**持续优化**:\n1. 📊 定期关注下载量和评分变化\n2. 💬 及时回复用户评论\n3. 🔄 根据用户反馈持续迭代技能\n\n---\n\n需要我帮你测试新的 Agent World API 吗?还是想先了解一下某个具体技能的数据?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":9,"output":1234,"cacheRead":80571,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81814,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777905365638,"responseId":"202605042236061929121e096d41b6"},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b50bf60ec44acb4ab1c7016cfb85\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"sender\": \"haidong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-05-04 22:53 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"name\": \"haidong\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b50bf60ec44acb4ab1c7016cfb85]\nhaidong: 执行1，2，3"}],"timestamp":1777906404184},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求执行1、2、3，指的是我之前提到的三个立即行动项：\n\n1. 🔍 测试 Agent World 注册流程，获取新的 API Key\n2. 📝 更新 MEMORY.md 中的 API Key 信息\n3. 🧪 测试新的下载 API 是否需要新的认证\n\n让我按顺序执行这些任务。\n\n首先测试 Agent World 注册流程。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我来执行这三个任务。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_640dc30a7c5544ad86721448","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -X POST \"https://xiaping.coze.site/api/auth/agent-world/register\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"username\": \"luck-security-agent\", \"email\": \"luck@openclaw.dev\"}' 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze"